## Installation

<details open>
<summary><b>Quick Install</b></summary>

**Install via pip**
> Requires Python 3.10+

```bash
pip install meine
```
</details>

<details>
<summary><b>From Source</b></summary>

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Balaji01-4D/meine
cd meine
pip install .
```
</details>

